>
> George, or anyone else, if I have a broken perimeter
> spring in the seat is there any particular advice about
> welding it?  It is, of course, thin and it is spring
> steel, so I am emboldened to ask.  I do not have a
> spot welder, so it will be MIG or stick if at all.
> (This is a flat metal strip around the outside of
